        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "Random order is used"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "Actions have a complete sequence",
      "explanation": "Totally ordered planning specifies a complete linear sequence of actions.",
      "difficulty": "easy"
    },
    {
      "id": "mcq-18",
      "question": "A heuristic is used in planning to:",
      "options": [
        {
          "key": "A",
          "text": "Represent states"
        },
        {
          "key": "B",
          "text": "Guide search toward goal"
        },
        {
          "key": "C",
          "text": "Define actions"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
